  "text": "This ratio score was introduced in [CITATION_1] . It basically discredits matches for which there are similar alternatives, and thus a higher likelihood of the match being incorrect. In line with [CITATION_2] we also make sure that the second-best match either has a different size, or originates from a different part of the image.",
